                            <p>Requirements for exporters’ exchange (Rials 28.28 per $1, as against
                                current rates of approximately Rials 19.5 equal $1): <table cols="2" rend="width: 50%" rendition="#center-block" rows="4">
                                    <row>
                                        <cell>Motor trucks</cell>
                                        <cell role="num">20%</cell>
                                    </row>
                                    <row>
                                        <cell>Passenger cars</cell>
                                        <cell role="num">20%</cell>
                                    </row>
                                    <row>
